sub_title: Masterplanning & Urban Design - Tourism planning & Destination design
summary:
With a portfolio spanning Europe, North Africa, the Middle East, Australia and Asia, I have a unique, global understanding of placemaking and the elements required to ensure long-term social, economic and environmental value for communities. 
Since joining WATG in 2005, I have worked in our London, US and Singapore offices, and design and lead projects of all scales â€“ from big complex new towns to smaller, integrated resorts and residential developments.
